Company Overview of GE Capital Aviation Services, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
GE Capital Aviation Services, Inc. provides commercial aircraft financing and leasing services . It offers operating lease and purchase leaseback options, and secured loans. The company also provides various productivity solutions, including spare engine leasing, aviation consulting, and spare parts financing and management services. Its portfolio includes narrow and wide body, cargo, and regional and turboprop aircrafts, as well as medium and heavy helicopters. The company serves airline customers worldwide. GE Capital Aviation Services, Inc. was founded in 1993 and is based in Stamford, Connecticut. The company has additional offices internationally. GE Capital Aviation Services, Inc. oper...
GE Capital Aviation Services, Inc. provides commercial aircraft financing and leasing services . It offers operating lease and purchase leaseback options, and secured loans. The company also provides various productivity solutions, including spare engine leasing, aviation consulting, and spare parts financing and management services. Its portfolio includes narrow and wide body, cargo, and regional and turboprop aircrafts, as well as medium and heavy helicopters. The company serves airline customers worldwide. GE Capital Aviation Services, Inc. was founded in 1993 and is based in Stamford, Connecticut. The company has additional offices internationally. GE Capital Aviation Services, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of GE Capital US Holdings, Inc.
