What Capital Aircraft Services does and why
Aviation is throwing us many challenges – from regulatory reform to exciting technological advances making avionic modifications a complex undertaking. Capital Aircraft Services tackles these challenges to design, supply and integrate new equipment into your aircraft.
We understand the variations between global regulator legislation, we are conversant with product availability and capability, we make the distinction between a minor and major modification and determine the most beneficial method of certification.
Capital Aircraft Services is the connecting piece of your avionic modification puzzle – simplifying this complex task.
 
